g.text: ArthurRank3Convo2 begins.

g.title: j2366204034
g.text: Ever sit there and think about how many people you've killed?

g.title: j3577106227
g.text: I try not to.

g.title: j1505069925
g.text: What a way to start a conversation.

g.title: j1624134431
g.text: Sometimes. Usually when I'm trying to fall asleep.

g.title: j85353577
g.text: I think about it like a high score.

g.title: j2579567552
g.text: I played that game for a while. But they find a way in.

g.title: j155705256
g.text: Heh. They don't promote soldiers for social skills.

g.title: j1143259377
g.text: Like counting sheep, right?

g.title: j3041661299
g.text: Whatever gets you through the nights, I suppose.

g.title: j1131229908
g.text: Do you need to talk?

g.title: j3432417302
g.text: Truth.

g.title: j3485520016
g.text: Eh, you seem to have done all right.

g.title: j3089471533
g.text: Worst. Sheep. Ever.

g.title: j77791185
g.text: What's a... "sheep?"

g.title: Chat ends.
g.text: Chat ends.

g.title: j461179446
g.text: I thought I did. Though I might be changing my mind.

g.title: j479853532
g.text: This is the bit I never understood. How do you start talking about this kind of bullshit?

g.title: j2863429234
g.text: Too kind.

g.title: j3828315128
g.text: +10 Chemistry

g.title: j1472112015
g.text: +10 Chemistry

g.title: j2837291695
g.text: Why?

g.title: j2927547779
g.text: Good call. [End.]

g.title: j385734674
g.text: I won't force you to talk if you don't want to.

g.title: j3527696658
g.text: I'll go first, then.

g.title: j2353149508
g.text: Not my job to figure that out for you.

g.title: j3985712149
g.text: Sol, I feel that.

g.title: j3724113574
g.text: Sol, that's bloody adorable. Thanks for the laugh.

g.title: j930562847
g.text: Thanks. We'll try this another time.

g.title: j894859913
g.text: I try not to think too much about what I've had to do to get through life. Because I don't have anybody to talk to about it.

g.title: j3874352369
g.text: +10 Chemistry

g.title: j1270814497
g.text: I only had myself to talk to.

g.title: j1487843466
g.text: Boolean ArthurSoldier is now true.

g.title: j1026702550
g.text: I've never even really had friends. You and the others are the closest I've ever come to... belonging somewhere.

g.title: j4272727990
g.text: How sad is that?

g.title: j3579496956
g.text: At least you've had the option to talk if you've wanted to. But hey. If you need me? I'm here.

g.title: j1309572175
g.text: I'm not sure I like it when you make sense.

g.title: j1818046523
g.text: +20 Chemistry

g.title: j538708567
g.text: I can't do this today. But thanks. This...means a lot.
